{"tid":2430223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「急徵探監物資！！！」在囚手足要零食同日用品！！！","createTime":"2021-03-02T19:48:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T12:06:36.000Z","uid":11055,"like":119,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":109,"replies":[{"pid":"268e54ca47eaab63b3f6af7f549727dbd2fa8b44","tid":2430223,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T19:48:01.000Z","msg":"【急徵物資】#幫手share呢個post 🙇<br />\n<br />\n因部分零食及日用品現時已無存貨，再次需要大家幫手，希望大家繼續幫手收集物資，我哋會盡快轉交畀在囚手足 🙏🙏<br />\n<br />\n以下物資只剩少量或已無存貨：<br />\n<br />\n－M&amp;M's （黑/黃包裝 40 克)<br />\n－魷魚絲（金龜嘜 7 克)<br />\n－沙爹牛肉片／豬肉片 （優之良品  5克)<br />\n<br />\n－潤手膏 （梨牌 80 毫升）<br />\n－牙膏 （黑人／高露潔 250 克）<br />\n－內褲（灰色）<br />\n－肥皂（LUX 藍色）<br />\n－洗頭水（花王飛逸 400 毫升）<br />\n－濕紙巾（滴露10片裝／詩樂氏每包共10片獨立包裝)<br />\n<br />\n早前收集嘅日用品及零食已陸續入畀手足，非常感謝大家幫手收集物資。歡迎pm我哋交收物資/將物資帶到辦事處，以便轉交手足親友；如探訪需要入物資，可以聯絡我哋約時間交收，費用全免!<br />\n<br />\n*物資包裝size需同「認可交來物品」清單中嘅圖片一模一樣，以懲教署官方資訊為準：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.csd.gov.hk/tc_chi/socialvisit/socialvisit_articles/ins_vis_guide_handin_articles.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.csd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fsocialvisit%2Fsocialvisit_articles%2Fins_vis_guide_handin_articles.html&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuvcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=aa89b30b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.csd.gov.hk/tc_chi/socialvisit/socialvisit_articles/ins_vis_guide_handin_articles.html</a><br />\n<br />\n#徵集物資﻿ ﻿#在囚手足﻿ ﻿#支援手足家屬<br />\n#巫啟航 #宏逸 #俊宏軒 #天逸 #hongkong #香港 #天水圍<br />\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━<br />\nPhone/Signal：9426 5060<br />\nE-mail：fleco@flecomo.hk<br />\nTelegram：@fleco_mkh<br />\nInstagram：fleco_mkh<br />\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━<br />\n宏逸社區關注群組 📣想俾意見，了解最新資訊！<br />\n✅加入Telegram群組：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/33rWYMo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33rWYMo&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuvcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=11114411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/33rWYMo</a>"},{"pid":"04c0eab8f3d60eccc9c6a5e49542476d85d2e7db","tid":2430223,"uid":11055,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"ci